trans-unit.source: Provides a minimal reader of incoming response return values for Web service clients implemented using HTTP but without SOAP.
trans-unit.target: Gir minimal leseren for innkommende svar returverdier for Web service-klienter implementert ved hjelp av HTTP, men uten SOAP.

trans-unit.source: AnyReturnReader and other classes in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols> namespace support the .NET Framework's implementations of Web services via the HTTP-GET and HTTP-POST operations.
trans-unit.target: AnyReturnReader og andre klasser i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>navneområdet støtter .NET Framework-implementeringer av webtjenester via HTTP-GET og HTTP-POST-operasjoner.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers serialize and deserialize, respectively, between the parameters or return objects of Web methods and the HTTP request or response streams.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere lesere serialisere og deserialisere henholdsvis mellom parameterne eller return objekter av Web-metoder og HTTP-forespørselen eller svar dataflytene.

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers use HTTP for transport but don't exchange messages using the SOAP standard.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere og lesere bruke HTTP til transport, men exchange ikke meldinger ved hjelp av SOAP-standard.

trans-unit.source: The AnyReturnReader class provides a minimal implementation of the interface of the abstract parent class <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>.You typically will not need to use AnyReturnReader directly.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AnyReturnReader gir en minimal implementering av grensesnittet abstrakte overordnede klasse <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>. Vanligvis ikke må du bruke AnyReturnReader direkte.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: When the Wsdl.exe tool generates client proxy code according to the HTTP-GET or HTTP-POST implementations, it applies the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute> to each Web method and by default sets the attribute's <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute.ReturnFormatter%2A> property to <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.XmlReturnReader>, another class derived from <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>.
trans-unit.target: Når verktøyet Wsdl.exe genererer proxy-Klientkoden i henhold til implementeringer HTTP-GET eller HTTP-POST, brukes <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute>til hver Web-metode, og som standard angir attributtets- <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute.ReturnFormatter%2A>egenskapen for å <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.XmlReturnReader>en annen klasse som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeReturnReader> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.XmlReturnReader> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute.ReturnFormatter%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns the parameter passed to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize*> method.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer parameteren som sendes til den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize*>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize*>

trans-unit.source: An initializer is an object passed as a parameter to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: En initialisering er et objekt som ble sendt som en parameter i <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader> class, the initializer is the instance referred to by the keyword `this`, unless the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo> parameter value has a void return type, in which case the initializer is set to `null`.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>klassen, er initialiseringen forekomsten av referert til av nøkkelordet `this`, med mindre den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo>parameterverdien har en ugyldig returtype, der store/små bokstaver i initialisering er satt til `null`.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: The GetInitializer method is invoked during service initialization.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetInitializer aktiveres under initialisering av tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Later, at the time a response is processed, the initializer <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader> object is passed to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize%2A> method of another <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader> instance.
trans-unit.target: Senere, da svar behandles, initialiseringen <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>objekt som er sendt til den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize%2A>-metoden til et annet <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: The other instance takes the call to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Read%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Den andre forekomsten tar kallet til den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Read%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Read%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"></xref> that indicates the Web method for which the initializer is obtained.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"> </xref> som angir Web-metoden i initialisering hentes.

trans-unit.source: The parameter passed to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize*> method.
trans-unit.target: {Parameteren sendt til den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize*>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.Initialize*>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The Initialize method does nothing.
trans-unit.target: I initialiseringsmetoden gjøre noe.

trans-unit.source: This method is invoked at the time a response is processed.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden aktiveres da svar er behandlet.

trans-unit.source: The input parameter, `initializer`, is another instance of <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>, obtained during client initialization.
trans-unit.target: Inndataparameteren `initializer`, er en annen forekomst av <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>, hentede under initialisering av klienten.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: Another instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader"></xref> class, on which the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.GetInitializer*> method was previously called.
trans-unit.target: En annen forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader"> </xref> klassen som den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.GetInitializer*>metoden tidligere ble kalt.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader.GetInitializer*>

trans-unit.source: Returns the input HTTP response stream.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den inngående HTTP-svar dataflyten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader> class's implementation of the Read method does no reading.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>klassens implementering av metoden lese støtter ikke lesing.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.AnyReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: Instead it simply returns the <xref:System.IO.Stream> object passed as a parameter.
trans-unit.target: I stedet bare returneres av <xref:System.IO.Stream>objekt sendt som en parameter.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: A representation of the HTTP response sent by a Web service, containing the output message for an operation.
trans-unit.target: En representasjon av HTTP-svar sendt av en webtjeneste, som inneholder utdatameldingen for en operasjon.

trans-unit.source: An output stream whose content is the body of the HTTP response represented by the `response` parameter.
trans-unit.target: En output-dataflyten filreferanser er meldingsteksten i HTTP-svar som representerer den `response` parameteren.

trans-unit.source: The input HTTP response stream.
trans-unit.target: Den inngående HTTP-svar dataflyten.
